  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies spawn every round and march toward your Crystal Tower.<br>Defend it against waves of increasingly stronger foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round, you’ll receive a gear draw ticket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use it to obtain random gear materials, and upgrade your equipment to higher tiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between enemy waves, there are moments of peace.<br>Take that time to enter the mine and collect valuable resources.<br>Mining provides various materials that help your character grow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 10 rounds, a powerful boss will appear.<br>These bosses are extremely tough.<br>If you're struggling to defeat one, check if you're lacking boss-specific equipment or abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the Unique tier and up, each piece of gear has its own skill.<br>Use these unique skills strategically to build the ultimate gear combinations.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/5f02e99d98358b2eda0556906b1c060c.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies spawn every round and march toward your Crystal Tower.<br>Defend it against waves of increasingly stronger foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/b9b20c508739626d4df7ccbea33b4a34.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each round, you’ll receive a gear draw ticket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use it to obtain random gear materials, and upgrade your equipment to higher tiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/10bc40719dd400b530cedd21eea15798.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between enemy waves, there are moments of peace.<br>Take that time to enter the mine and collect valuable resources.<br>Mining provides various materials that help your character grow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/877ee6ed259bc64cd8d6274c6f138087.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 10 rounds, a powerful boss will appear.<br>These bosses are extremely tough.<br>If you're struggling to defeat one, check if you're lacking boss-specific equipment or abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.poster.avif?t=1751110489\" width=800 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.webm?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3557100/extras/97c0be06f9c20752dfeab0da33d30d65.mp4?t=1751110489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From the Unique tier and up, each piece of gear has its own skill.<br>Use these unique skills strategically to build the ultimate gear combinations.</p>",
